title: The Gary Null Show
content:
A continuing series on fascism in the United States, with US Representative Alan Grayson. Alan Mark Grayson is the... <!--more--> United States Representative for Florida’s 9th congressional district and a member of the Democratic Party.
He previously served as Representative for Florida’s 8th congressional district from 2009 to 2011.
Eight months into the 113th Congress, Rep.
Alan Grayson has passed more amendments than any other Member of the US House of Representatives, Democrat or Republican.
